:INFO
Build and Sell Notion Templates
Notion templates are a low-overhead digital product with strong demand. A well-designed template that solves a specific workflow problem can sell steadily with minimal maintenance.

:COUNTER.half
27 USD
Typical price point for a premium Notion template
|
:COUNTER.half
100 Sales
First revenue milestone worth targeting

:PATH
Design Phase
Identify a specific workflow problem. Build the template in Notion with real content as a demo. Use linked databases, formulas, and views to show full capability.

:PATH
Package Phase
Duplicate the template and clear demo content. Write a setup guide. Create a cover image and feature screenshots. Record a two-minute walkthrough video.

:PATH
Sell Phase
List on Gumroad with a clear title, benefit-focused description, and preview screenshots. Share on Twitter, Reddit, and Notion-specific communities.

:CHECKLIST
Template Launch Checklist
[ ] Identify target workflow and user type
[ ] Build full template with demo data
[ ] Create clean version for delivery
[ ] Write setup and usage guide
[ ] Design cover and preview images
[ ] Record walkthrough video
[ ] Set up Gumroad product page
[ ] Price with a free tier or free sample included
[ ] Post launch thread on Twitter

:NOTE
Offer a stripped-down free version of your template to build your email list. Free downloads convert to paid buyers over time, especially if you follow up with tips for getting more value from the template.

:LINK
https://gumroad.com
Gumroad: sell digital products directly to your audience